thread.title: BRIEF-‍Horizons ETFs Management (Canada) Files Final Prospectus To Launch Marijuana ETF

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-‍Horizons ETFs Management (Canada) Files Final Prospectus To Launch Marijuana ETF
text:
Feb 6 (Reuters) - Horizons ETFs Management (Canada) Inc:
* ‍HORIZONS ETFS MANAGEMENT (CANADA) INC - FILED FINAL PROSPECTUS TO LAUNCH HORIZONS EMERGING MARIJUANA GROWERS INDEX ETF
* HORIZONS ETFS MANAGEMENT (CANADA) INC - UNITS OF HORIZONS EMERGING MARIJUANA GROWERS INDEX ETF CONDITIONALLY APPROVED FOR LISTING
* HORIZONS ETFS MANAGEMENT (CANADA) INC-HORIZONS EMERGING MARIJUANA GROWERS INDEX ETF UNITS TO BEGIN TRADING ON AEQUITAS NEO EXCHANGE ON OR ABOUT FEB 14 Source text for Eikon: (Bengaluru Newsroom: +91 806 749 1136)
